Privacy Policy.
No personal information is collected in this application.
In this application, device identifiers are used to show you advertising related to your preferences. 
By using this application, we consider that you accept the use of these identifiers.
By means of our privacy policy we inform you of the proper conditions of use on this site. The use of these implies your full and unreserved acceptance of each and every one of the provisions included in this Legal Notice, so if you do not agree with any of the conditions set forth herein, you should not use and / or access this site or application.
